@startuml
!theme plain

class DataPreprocessor {
  +load_data(file: str)
  +clean_data()
  +encode_categoricals()
  +impute_missing()
}

class ModelTrainer {
  +train_models()
  +evaluate_models()
  +select_best_model()
}

class Explainability {
  +run_shap()
  +run_lime()
}

class Predictor {
  +predict(input_data)
  +save_results()
}

DataPreprocessor --> ModelTrainer : prepares data
ModelTrainer --> Predictor : provides best model
Predictor --> Explainability : sends predictions
@enduml
